summary_markdown: This data presents a comparative analysis of "Crest switchers," categorizing them based on their agreement or disagreement with a particular statement or proposition. The structure is a simple dichotomy, illustrating the proportion of individuals within this group who fall into each of the two opposing stances. Specifically, 68% of Crest switchers are shown to agree, while the remaining 32% disagree. This highlights a clear majority favoring agreement among this identified consumer segment.
